{"parse":{"title":"Battle Drills","pageid":769,"revid":36645,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"custom-tabs-default custom-tabs\"><span class=\"active-tab\"><strong class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Overview</strong></span><span class=\"inactive-tab\"><a href=\"/wiki/Battle_Drills/Current_%26_Past_Battle_Drills\" title=\"Battle Drills/Current &amp; Past Battle Drills\">Current &amp; Past Battle Drills</a></span><span class=\"inactive-tab\"><a href=\"/wiki/Battle_Drills/Rewards\" title=\"Battle Drills/Rewards\">Rewards</a></span></div>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-wikia pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">Battle Drills</h2>\n\n<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\" data-source=\"image\">\n\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/f/f7/Battle_Drill_Mode_Card.png/revision/latest?cb=20240416065738\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Battle Drill Mode Card\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/f/f7/Battle_Drill_Mode_Card.png/revision/latest?cb=20240416065738\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/f/f7/Battle_Drill_Mode_Card.png/revision/latest?cb=20240416065738 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/f/f7/Battle_Drill_Mode_Card.png/revision/latest?cb=20240416065738 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Battle Drill Mode Card\" width=\"221\" height=\"358\" data-image-key=\"Battle_Drill_Mode_Card.png\" data-image-name=\"Battle Drill Mode Card.png\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t\n\t<section class=\"pi-item pi-panel pi-border-color wds-tabber\">\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"wds-tabs\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDetails\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"type\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Type</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><span class=\"new\" title=\"PvE Battle Mode (page does not exist)\" data-uncrawlable-url=\"L3dpa2kvUHZFX0JhdHRsZV9Nb2RlP2FjdGlvbj1lZGl0JnJlZGxpbms9MQ==\">PvE</span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"group\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Groups</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><ul><li><span class=\"new\" title=\"Routine Battle Modes (page does not exist)\" data-uncrawlable-url=\"L3dpa2kvUm91dGluZV9CYXR0bGVfTW9kZXM/YWN0aW9uPWVkaXQmcmVkbGluaz0x\">Routine</span></li><li><span class=\"new\" title=\"Guild Battle Modes (page does not exist)\" data-uncrawlable-url=\"L3dpa2kvR3VpbGRfQmF0dGxlX01vZGVzP2FjdGlvbj1lZGl0JnJlZGxpbms9MQ==\">Guild</span></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t</section>\n\n\n\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p><br />\n</p><p><b>Battle Drill</b> is a periodic <a href=\"/wiki/Guild\" title=\"Guild\">Guild</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Battle_Mode\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle Mode\">Battle Mode</a> available to all players in a guild who have cleared AFK Stage 50. You can earn Reputation Treasure and Treasure Keys to unlock rewards. The cumulative performance of your Guild will determine their placement in the Battle Drill Rankings.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Schedule\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Schedule</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Basic_Requirements\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Basic Requirements</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Basics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Basics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Rules\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rules</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Difficulty\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Difficulty</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Stamina\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Stamina</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Season_Levels\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Season Levels</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Guild_Loot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Guild Loot</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Chest_of_Valor\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chest of Valor</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Reputation_Treasure\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reputation Treasure</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Buffs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Buffs</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Round_Buff\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Round Buff</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Change_History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Change History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Schedule\">Schedule</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>For Guilds in the Starter Season, they will participate in three rounds of Battle drills. Guilds in Season 1 onwards will participate in six rounds of Battle Drills in each season. <i>Full details including the interactive maps for all 7 battle drill maps can be found in the Current &amp; Past Battle Drills tab.</i> For example, the <b><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://afk-journey.fandom.com/wiki/Map:Shadowfrost\">\ud83d\udd17 Shadowfrost (Interactive Map)</a></b> is shown on the right.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb mw-halign-right show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 400px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/3/39/Battle_Drill_Shadowfrost_Interactive_Map_Example.png/revision/latest?cb=20250414123607\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Shadowfrost Interactive Map\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/3/39/Battle_Drill_Shadowfrost_Interactive_Map_Example.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20250414123607\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"359\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Battle Drill Shadowfrost Interactive Map Example.png\" data-image-key=\"Battle_Drill_Shadowfrost_Interactive_Map_Example.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Battle_Drill_Shadowfrost_Interactive_Map_Example.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Shadowfrost Interactive Map</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Basic_Requirements\">Basic Requirements</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Basics\">Basics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Battle Drills Rankings will include all Guilds that participated in Battle Drills and occupied at least a passage or stronghold within a round. Guilds will be ranked according to the number of occupied Boss Strongholds and then sorted according to the total damage dealt to Boss in this round.</li>\n<li>A new Battle Drills Rankings will be published when the next round starts.</li>\n<li>Should a Guild disband, its ranking will be reserved, yet the details will not be available anymore.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rules\">Rules</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Battle Drills have two stages: a truce phase and a combat phase. During the truce, you can enter Battle Drills to view the enemy formation and plan your own attacks. During the combat phase, you can challenge the enemies. Combat types include Passage Brawl, Stronghold battles, and Boss battles.</li>\n<li>You need to depart from your camp and challenge passages and strongholds linked to the camp</li>\n<li>You will need to use Stamina to challenge passages and strongholds. You will earn rewards such as Gold and Treasure Keys. Treasure Keys are used to open the Chest of Valor.</li>\n<li>You share the progress in challenging passages and strongholds with other Guild members. Once all passages and strongholds have been captured, you will be able to challenge the final boss.</li>\n<li>Hero levels will be affected by the baseline level in the Battle Drills mode. Check the Command Center to view the current baseline level. When a hero's level is below the baseline, they will be automatically upgraded to match the baseline. However, if a hero's level surpasses the baseline, 10% of the excess will be added to the baseline level, setting their actual level for Battle Drills.</li>\n<li>After you change your Guild, you can still participate in Battle Drills in the new guild. If you have participated in Battle Drills of your former Guild today, you can participate in the Battle Drills of the new Guild the following day.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Difficulty\">Difficulty</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>There are three modes in Battle Drills: Stout Recruit, Seasoned Challenger, and Restless Warrior.</li>\n<li>Defeat the final boss in Stout Recruit to advance to the next mode, Seasoned Challenger.</li>\n<li>In Seasoned Challeger mode, you will challenge the Battle Drills again with all buffs, camp skills, and camp levels obtained through the previous mode. Defeat the final boss again to advance to Restless Warrior.</li>\n<li>In Restless Warrior mode, you will face a never-ending challenge against a final boss that respawns after you defeat it until the end of the current round of Battle Drills.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stamina\">Stamina</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>Upon initial deployment, you start with 10 Stamina.</li>\n<li>Stamina recovers by 10 daily at 08:00 (UTC+8), storing up to 30 Stamina.</li>\n<li>Camps at Level 90 or above recover an extra 5 Stamina daily, storing up to 45.</li>\n<li>Hero Stamina Rules:\n<dl><dd><ul><li>Each hero recovers 1 Stamina daily, storing up to 3 Stamina.</li>\n<li>Deploying a hero to battle costs 1 Stamina: 1 Hero Stamina and Daily Stamina.</li></ul></dd></dl></li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Season_Levels\">Season Levels</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Season Level for the current round of Battle Drills will be adjusted to Level 400. Hero Equipment Levels are adjusted to match Hero Level.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Guild_Loot\">Guild Loot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chest_of_Valor\">Chest of Valor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>You can use Treasure Keys to unlock the Chest of Valor and receive various rewards, including a chance to obtain Diamonds. Treasure Keys can be obtained from Reputation Treasures or by fighting the guards and bosses in Battle Drills.</li>\n<li>Treasure Keys that have not been used before the next round of Battle Drills starts will be converted into rewards and issued via mail.</li></ol>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reputation_Treasure\">Reputation Treasure</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D10&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>You can earn points through quests to increase your Reputation Level.</li>\n<li>Increasing your Reputation Level will unlock brand new rewards.</li>\n<li>All unclaimed rewards will be sent to you via mail after each round of Battle Drills.</li></ol>\n<p><i>Full details of rewards given can be found in the Rewards Tab.</i>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Buffs\">Buffs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D11&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Round_Buff\">Round Buff</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D12&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ol><li>You can get buffs through specific camp choices, occupation of different strongholds, etc.</li>\n<li>Gained buffs will last until the end of the current round of Battle Drills.</li>\n<li>The buffs introduced so far is listed below:</li></ol>\n<table class=\"article-table article-table sortable alternating-colors-table mw-collapsible\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Icon</th>\n<th>Buff</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n<th>Maps\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Defense Master</td>\n<td><b>Full</b>: Extends shield duration for all allies and enemies by 50%, increases allied heroes\u2019 Phys DEF and Magic DEF by 40%.<br /><b>Lite</b>: Increases Phys DEF and Magic DEF by 35% for allied heroes.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Divine Punishment</td>\n<td>Allies\u2019 normal attacks deal additional Phys DMG equal to 5% of the target\u2019s max HP (max 80% of caster\u2019s ATK).</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Energy Flow</td>\n<td>Grants 50 Haste and restores 40 Energy per second for allies.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Focus Hit</td>\n<td>Grants all allies' normal attacks 35 Crit and increases allied heroes' ATK SPD by 4 for each 10 DEF Penetration.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Hot Pursuit</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' damage dealt by 150% in non-Boss Stronghold battles, triggered if \u22642 non-summoned enemies at battle start.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Instant Momentum</td>\n<td>At the start of battle, each allied hero gains 600 Energy and 40 Haste for 6s.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Iron Resolve</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' damage dealt by 250% in non-Boss Stronghold battles, triggered if &gt;4 non-summoned enemies at battle start.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Moment of Glory</td>\n<td><b>Full</b>: When ally ULTS, restores 5% of Max HP to allies and increases their ATK by 25% and Crit by 30 for 3s. Stacks.<br /><b>Lite</b>: Whenever an ally casts an Ultimate, restores 5% of max HP to all allies and increases their ATK by 15% and Crit by 10 for 3s. This effect can stack.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Rising Valor</td>\n<td>Increases allied heroes' ATK SPD by 4 for each normal attack dealt by them, up to 200.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Spell Mastery</td>\n<td>Increases allies\u2019 non-normal attack damage by 150% and grants 40 Crit to these non-normal attacks.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Strength in Unity</td>\n<td>Stuns all enemies for 2s for every 5 Ultimates cast by the allied team, dealing magic damage equal to 8% of each target\u2019s max HP (up to 60% of Team ATK).</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Superiority</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' damage dealt by 50% in Boss Stronghold battles; Supreme+ Heroes gain an extra 250% damage boost with Lvl. 15 Exclusive Equipment.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Superior Skill</td>\n<td>Increases allies\u2019 non-normal attack damage by 150%; stacks when converged.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Trailblazer</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' damage dealt by 250% in Passage Brawl.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>True Potential</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' damage dealt by 150% in Elite Stronghold battles.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Versatile Style</td>\n<td>Increases all allies' Phys DEF by 25%, Magic DEF by 25%, and ATK by 15%.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Upload?wpDestFile=Icon.png\" class=\"new\" title=\"File:Icon.png\"><span class=\"mw-file-element mw-broken-media\" data-width=\"32\">File:Icon.png</span></a></span></td>\n<td>Wild Might</td>\n<td><b>Full</b>: Extends shield duration for all allies and enemies by 50%, increases allied heroes\u2019 ATK by 20%.<br /><b>Lite</b>: Increases ATK by 20% for Allied Heroes.</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Change_History\">Change History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FBattle_Drills%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D13&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"change-history\"><div class=\"change-history-header\"><div>Released in <b><a href=\"/wiki/Version/1.0\" title=\"Version/1.0\">Version 1.0</a></b></div><div>[<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://afk-journey.fandom.com/wiki/Battle_Drills/Change_History?action=edit\">Edit History</a>]</div></div><div class=\"change-history-content standard-border\"><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.6.1\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.6.1\">Version 1.6.1</a>\n<ul><li>Passage brawls removed from the battlefield maps as well as from Reputation Quests. Camp Level rewards and Reputation Level requirements adjusted as a result.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.4.4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.4.4\">Version 1.4.4</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Fixed an issue where damage in Battle Drills was abnormal and caused severe lag during battles.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.4.1\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.4.1\">Version 1.4.1</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Added new battlefield: Verdshroom Grove.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.1.14\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.1.14\">Version 1.1.14</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Added new battlefield: Desolate Grounds.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.1.13\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.1.13\">Version 1.1.13</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Adjusted instance design and unlock nodes, optimizing interface experience, and significantly balancing difficulty and reward values.</li>\n<li>Fixed abnormal ranking sorting issues in some cases in Rankings.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.11\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.11\">Version 1.0.11</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Reduced the overall difficulty of battles.</li>\n<li>Optimized certain interfaces.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.10\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.10\">Version 1.0.10</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Heroes deployed by the Command Center can now be changed.</li>\n<li>Optimized the interface experience.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.9\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.9\">Version 1.0.9</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>The enhancement item, Impure Divine Ash, can be obtained through Reputation Treasure.</li>\n<li>Added Individual Loot selection. Players can now choose the type of resources, allowing for personalized loot selection.</li>\n<li>Adjusted Treasure Key drop rules for a more reasonable output.</li>\n<li>Adjusted the Gold rewards.</li>\n<li>Bosses in Restless Warrior mode can now be defeated and immediately respawn after death.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.7\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.7\">Version 1.0.7</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Remodeled. This mode will be periodically available as an event and is designed to maintain balanced difficulty using a benchmark level. Both the mode itself and the event rewards had undergone substantial changes.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.4\">Version 1.0.4</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Adjusted the strength of monsters. Removed the Member Chest level so that players can open chests as soon as they get keys. Combined with other related adjustments, Battle Drills no longer drop Dew Selection Chests. They drop equipment instead. Because of this, the chance of getting various types of rewards from Member Chests was also adjusted accordingly. The collection time for Team Chests has been adjusted from Monday at 20:00 to Monday at 00:00 UTC.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.3\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.3\">Version 1.0.3</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Improved the Assist Team's energy recovery efficiency.</li>\n<li>Added Dew Choice Chest to the dropped rewards.</li>\n<li>The Arena Stats of Exclusive Weapon no longer took effect in Battle Drills.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0.1\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0.1\">Version 1.0.1</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Fixed an issue where the damage ranking in the Weekly Battle Report was inconsistent with the damage ranking in the Battle Drills Rankings.</li></ul>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Version_1.0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version 1.0\">Version 1.0</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Battle Drills was released.</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"clear:both; margin:0; padding:0;\"></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260608082718\nCache expiry: 2592000\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show\u2010toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.093 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.137 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 515/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 17804/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5210/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/100\nExpensiv